## Standing Directive: Zero-Physical-Access Deployment

**Never suggest plugging in a monitor, keyboard, or mouse.** SSH is the only access method. If SSH is lost, the unit is bricked. Every configuration decision must prioritize SSH reliability above all else. Wired ethernet only — WiFi permanently disabled. Claude owns the configuration criteria and must proactively harden for 100% remote reliability, building in preconditions and fallbacks before every risky operation.

